{
  "arquivo": "ca05_mv1_02",
  "total": 80,
  "dialogos": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "I did some good shopping.\\nNow if only the right person could come along,\\nthen it would be perfect.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "We wouldn't be so lucky. ",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Hmm? Isn't that Nino and Yotsuba?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Oh, the perfect person has arrived.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Huh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "What's going on?\\nAre you planning something?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Ah...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Hee-hee-hee!\\nYou're quite brave, Uesugi-san.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "But aren't you being overly cautious?\\nI'm not going to do anything weird.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "N-no, I didn't mean to suspect you\\nor anything, Nino.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "You acted on impulse.\\nThe power of love, I see.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "U-um!\\nAnyway, is there anything you want from me?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "We want you to try this on.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "What's this?\\nIt looks like a metal rod.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "This is a traditional Okinawan hairpin,\\ncalled a 'jiifaa.'",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "A hairpin, huh?\\nIt's the first time I've seen this shape.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "I saw it at the store and fell in love with it.\\nSo, Itsuki, can you let me try it on your hair?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "That's a bit out of nowhere, isn't it?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "It's fine.\\nYou have long hair, so it'll look good on you.\\nIt'll be a fun challenge.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "*sigh*\\nI guess it's okay.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Is it really possible to do it here?\\nWe don't even have a comb or a mirror.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "I can easily put it together.\\nIf it's a more complicated style,\\nthen we might need hairpins.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Oh, that's how it is.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Alright, I'm done!\\nIt turned out really nice.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Wow, you're quite talented.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "It's sooo cute!\\nItsuki, it really suits you!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Th-thank you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Um... F-Futaro, what do you think?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "What do I think...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Does it suit me?\\nI want to hear your opinion, as my...boyfriend.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Huh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "My, oh my.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Ooh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(B-boyfriend...\\n Isn't that cheating, asking me that way?)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Come on, Uesugi-san!\\nShe wants your opinion! Do tell!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...It's not bad.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "That's pretty vague, ya know.\\nDoes that mean it doesn't suit me?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "No! That's not what I mean! I just couldn't judge\\nwell because I'm not used to seeing you with\\nyour hair up... Um, you look good.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Well, if that's the case, just say so.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Sorry...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "But, thank you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "It's kind of a fresh look.\\nI don't usually get to see you\\nwith your hair up like that.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "That doesn't answer my question\\nabout whether it looks good on me or not.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Ah, well, um...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Or, do you not like this hairstyle,\\nFutaro?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 45,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...No, I think it's nice.\\nIt suits you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 46,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Is that so.\\nWell, then I'll try wearing my hair up like this \\nfrom time to time. ",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 47,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "It looks really good on you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 48,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "R-really?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 49,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Really.\\nI mean...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I'm a bit...entranced by it.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 51,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "!...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 52,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Oh my GOSH, that was so smooth...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 53,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "It's kind of embarrassing to watch.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 54,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Sh-shut up!\\nI was just giving her my opinion like she asked!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 55,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "A-anyway, I'll try this hairstyle occasionally.\\nBut only in front of you, Futaro...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 56,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "O-oh, is that so?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 57,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Thanks, Nino.\\nI'll give this back now.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 58,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "You seem pretty happy.\\nIs it because Fu-kun complimented you?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 59,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "W-well...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 60,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Of course. That's only natural, right?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 61,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "...Yeah. ",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 62,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 63,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Alright, you want to try it next, Fu-kun?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 64,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "You tell me. Look at the length of my hair. ",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 65,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Fine, we'll just stretch it out!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 66,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Don't be ridiculous!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 67,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Uesugi-kun with long hair...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 68,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...I just remembered, Nino, \\nweren't you the one that said long hair would look gross on me?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 69,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Oh, I did say that, didn't I?\\nCould it be that you're still holding a grudge?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 70,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "No, not really. I just believe in my potential.\\nThere's a possibility that long hair could suit me!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 71,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "That's right! I think it would look good on you!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 72,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "WHAAA?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 73,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Uesu%p-2;――%p; Futaro, there's infinite potential in you.\\nYou could even let your hair flow in the wind!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 74,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Anyone can do that.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 75,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "N-no, that's not what I mean!\\nUmm...uhh...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 76,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "A-anyway, I think it would suit you!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 77,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Hmm, it just might, you know?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 78,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "It definitely would!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 79,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Why is Itsuki getting so worked up over my hair...?)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    }
  ]
}